Please enter the work type you want to create? (Eg., Bug, Task, Epic, Story, Feature,
Request)
2. What is the priority of the defect? (We can set Medium as default)
3. What is the severity of the defect? (We can set Minor as default)
4. What is the baseline version in which the defect is detected? (Eg., v1.1)
5. What is the summary of the defect? (give a one line description of the defect)
6. Please give the detailed description of the defect (with Steps to reproduce, Expected
behavior and actual behavior)
7. Please give the platform details in which the defect is seen (Eg., Amidala Cable DE,
Amidala Satellite DE)
8. Can you please provide the intermittent details of the defect observed? (E.g., Highly
intermittent - rarely reproducible, Intermittent - 50% reproducible, Not Intermittent -
100% reproducible)
9. What kind of impact will the customer have because of this defect?
10. Do you have any logs captured for this defect? If yes, can you please upload?
11. Do you also have any video or picture that supports the understanding of the defect?
12. Is this a regression? (i.e., For any *test* that has previously passed, and now fails.)
13. Is this a new functionality?
